    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels at MRL 2. The six not-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out per ASME V&V 40 Table 5 requirements for MRL 2 Class II devices. Validation evidence demonstrates CFD-predicted relative hemolysis index satisfies RH < 1.0 at all five operating points with mean absolute error 8.3%. Mesh convergence confirmed with GCI < 2.1%. Code verification passed. The screening sensitivity evaluation of boundary condition perturbations provides additional confidence in result robustness. The credibility assessment team unanimously accepts the simulation evidence as sufficient to support the regulatory submission decision.",
